ild into MAI models for cost-effective AI workflows, especially via Foundry and MAI Playground?\n- **Agentic ROI**: Can Microsoft’s autonomous agents translate into measurable productivity gains and justify the rising expectations investors are placing on AI?\n- **Ecosystem expansion**: The interplay between internal models (MAI) and Azure AI services—as well as third-party specializations and global cloud investments—will determine Microsoft’s enterprise AI momentum this year.\n\nLet me know if you'd like a deeper dive into any of these developments—technical details, enterprise use cases, or comparative breakdowns across AI model providers.","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/04/02/microsoft-takes-on-ai-rivals-with-three-new-foundational-models/","start_index":640,"end_index":758,"title":"Microsoft takes on AI rivals with three new foundational ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.ai/news/today-were-announcing-3-new-world-class-mai-models-available-in-foundry/","start_index":925,"end_index":1041,"title":"Today we're announcing 3 new world class MAI models, available in ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.ai/news/today-were-announcing-3-new-world-class-mai-models-available-in-foundry/","start_index":1180,"end_index":1296,"title":"Today we're announcing 3 new world class MAI models, available in ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/04/02/microsoft-takes-on-ai-rivals-with-three-new-foundational-models/","start_index":1535,"end_index":1653,"title":"Microsoft takes on AI rivals with three new foundational ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://tech-insider.org/microsoft-mai-in-house-ai-models-openai-2026/","start_index":1853,"end_index":1945,"title":"Microsoft In-House AI Models: MAI Strategy vs OpenAI (2026)"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://winbuzzer.com/2026/04/03/microsoft-launches-3-in-house-ai-models-to-challenge-openai-google-xcxwbn/","start_index":2174